Wannan ya faru ne saboda shirin sauya sunan majalisa zuwa majalisa ta Wales.
AMs sun shiga cikin tsarin siyasa wanda ake damuwa cewa zai iya haifar da ban dariya.
Wani ma'aikacin AM ya ce tawagarsa ta damu da cewa tana amfani da kalmomin Twp da Pwp.
Ga masu karatu a waje na Welsh: A Welsh, kalmar twp tana nufin wuta, kuma pwp tana nufin yiwuwar.
Plaid AM ta ce kungiyar ba ta da farin ciki kuma ta ba da shawara kan wasu zaɓuɓɓuka.
Wani masanin farar hula Welsh ya ce tawagarsa ta kasance mai bude ido ga sauya sunan, amma kamar yadda aka ambata, gajerun kalmomi ne da suka sauka daga MWP zuwa Moffat.
A wannan mahallin, haruffan w suna karantawa daidai da yadda ake furta yaren Turanci na Jaxiah ga u.
