Game da batun sunayen AMs, kwamitin ya goyi bayan 'yan majalisar Wales ko WMPs, amma zaɓin MWP ya sami mafi yawan goyon baya a cikin shawarwarin jama'a.
A bayyane yake cewa AMs suna neman wani zaɓi, amma wannan kariya ta kai ga yanke shawara a cikin watan Disamba wanda zai iya haifar da ciwon kai ga Ofishin Shugaban kasa, Elin Jones, wanda ake sa ran zai sanya dokar canza sunan a cikin makonni.
