Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a Indonesia
A cewar jami'an, aƙalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afku a birnin Palu, Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, kuma adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Saboda an yanke sadarwa, jami'an ceto ba su iya samun wani bayani daga yankin Donggala da ke arewacin Palu ba, wanda ke kusa da girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.5 mai karfin gaske.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin Sulawesi ta tsakiya ne, yana kan iyakar bakin teku a gabar yammacin Sulawesi, tare da yawan jama'a 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
Birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwarsa lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka afkawa.
Donggala ƙasa ce mai sarrafawa wacce ke da iyaka mai yawa a cikin gabar teku sama da kilomita 300 a tsakiyar Sulawesi.
Ƙasar da ke ƙarƙashin wannan iko ita ce yankin da ke ƙarƙashin gundumar, tare da yawan jama'a 299,200 a cikin 2017.
Fishing da kuma noma sune manyan abubuwan tattalin arziki na Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, musamman yankin Donggala Coast.
Ana kuma yin amfani da karkarar nickel a wannan lardin, amma yawancin suna tattare da Morowali a bakin tekun Sulawesi.
A cewar hukumar kula da bala'i ta Indonesia, tsibirin Palu da Donggala sun sha wahala daga tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata.
A shekarar 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane sama da 200 kuma ya lalata daruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Wani tsunami ya kuma afkawa yammacin Donggala a shekarar 1996, inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin zagayen girgizar kasa na Pacific kuma tana fama da girgizar kasa.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai girma a gabar yamma ta lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin tsibirin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya mamaye ƙasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Tekun Indiya.
2005: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa gabar yamma ta Somatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias a bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 6.8 ta afkawa kudu maso gabashin tsibirin Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya afkawa cikin gabar teku ta kudu maso gabashin, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afkawa kusa da Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 sun mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai a Somatra, ta haifar da tsunami mai zurfin mita 10, ta lalata kauyuka da yawa, ta kashe mutane 300.
2016: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya a lardin Aceh, wanda ya haifar da lalacewa da firgici mai ƙarfi yayin da aka tunatar da mutane game da lalacewar girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na 2004.
Babu tsunami da ya barke a yanzu, duk da haka, sama da mutane 100 sun mutu sakamakon fashewar ginin.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, ta kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
