An zargi Saipov, mai shekaru 30 da haihuwa da amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don yin fashin kan titin keke a kan titin West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan wanda ya jefa masu hawa da kuma masu hawa a kan titin sa a watan Oktoba.
Don tabbatar da gaskiyar hukuncin kisa, mai gabatar da kara zai bayyana cewa Saipov ya kashe "da gangan" mutane takwas da kuma yi musu mummunan rauni "da gangan", a cewar sanarwar da aka gabatar a cikin Kotun ta Kudu ta New York.
A cewar takardun kotun, hukuncin kisa ne a kan duka biyun.
Makonni bayan harin, wani alkalin kotun tarayya ya yanke wa Saipov hukunci kan zargin 22 da ake yi masa, ciki har da laifin kisan kai guda takwas a cikin laifin cinikayya da aka yi amfani da shi a cikin hukumomin tarayya a cikin laifin aikata laifuka da kuma aikata laifuka da lalata motoci.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci "dabara da kuma taka tsantsan", suna bayyana yadda Saipov ya aiwatar da shi a matsayin "matsananci mai tsanani da rashin ɗabi'a".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi rauni da kuma lalata danginsa da abokansaDiego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco", a cikin bayanin kula.
Wadanda aka kashe su biyar 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekara goma kenan da suka shige tun lokacin da Kananan Hukumomin Kudancin New York suka yanke hukuncin kisa.
An yanke wa Khalid Barnes hukuncin kisa kan wasu masu rarraba miyagun ƙwayoyi, amma an yanke masa hukuncin rai a kurkuku a watan Satumbar 2009.
Kwanan nan an yi kisa a cikin New York Federal case a 1953 ga Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata, kuma an kashe su bayan an yanke musu hukunci kan yin aiki ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
Dukansu Rosenbergs an kashe su biyu ta hanyar wutar lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
A cewar takardun kotun, Saipov, wanda asalinsa Uzbekistan ne, ya nuna rashin kudi a cikin kwanaki da bayan harin.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya gaya wa masu binciken cewa yana jin daɗi game da abin da ya yi.
A cewar zargin, Saipov ya shaidawa hukumomi cewa an yi masa wahayi zuwa kai harin ne bayan ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya kuma nemi a nuna tutar ISIS a dakinsa na asibiti.
Ya amsa zargin cewa bai da laifi a kan zargin 22 na wannan lamarin.
David Patton, mai kare jama'a na tarayya da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce sun yi matukar takaici da hukuncin da hukumomi suka yanke.
Patton ya ce: "Muna ganin cewa yanke shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar amsa ga wadanda aka zarge da aikata laifin da ke kurkuku ba tare da yiwuwar sakewa ba zai iya kawo karshen wahalar da ake samu a kan wadannan abubuwan ga duk wanda ya ke da hannu.
Lauyoyin kare Saipov sun bukaci hukuma da kada ta nemi hukuncin kisa.
