Ruwa da ruwan sama: Ruwa yana raguwa a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Rahoton kwanan nan daga Hukumar Kifi da Dabbobin Jihar Florida ya nuna cewa an samu raguwar yawan zakoki a wasu yankunan yankin Tampa Bay.
FWC ta ce an samu karuwar jama'a a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier - wanda ya nuna cewa an samu raguwar jama'a.
Ruwan da aka yi wa zakoki na ruwa ya yi taɓarɓarewa da nisan mil 130 daga arewacin Pinellas Coast zuwa kudu maso gabashin Lee County.
Za a iya samun ɓarnar a kusan mil 10 daga bakin teku a Hillsborough County, amma a cikin ƙasa da mako guda da suka gabata.
An kuma lura da ruwan sama a Pakistan.
An ruwaito matsakaicin taro a cikin ko bakin tekun Pinellas County a makon da ya gabata daga ƙananan zuwa manyan taro a cikin kogin Hillsborough County, manyan taro a cikin Manatee County, manyan taro a Sarasota, manyan taro a cikin Charlotte County, manyan taro a cikin ko'ina cikin Lee County, ƙananan taro a cikin Collier County.
An samu ci gaba da samun ciwon huhu a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da Collier Counties.
Ba a taba samun rahoton cutar ta hanyar numfashi a yankin Florida ba a makon da ya gabata.
